                    <h2 class="rich_media_title" id="activity-name">
                        谁是真正的“高潜力人才”？80%的企业都选错了 
                    </h2>
                    <div class="rich_media_meta_list">
                                                <span id="copyright_logo" class="rich_media_meta meta_original_tag">原创</span>
                        						                        <em id="post-date" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text">2017-04-06</em>

                                                <em class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text">HBR</em>
                                                <a class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_link rich_media_meta_nickname" href="##" id="post-user">哈佛商业评论</a>
                        <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text rich_media_meta_nickname">哈佛商业评论</span>

                        <div id="js_profile_qrcode" class="profile_container" style="display:none;">
                            <div class="profile_inner">
                                <strong class="profile_nickname">哈佛商业评论</strong>
                                <img class="profile_avatar" id="js_profile_qrcode_img" src="" alt="">

